 more professional and help you easily create a wide range of cocktails.</p><p><br></p><p>A <a href="https://www.minimax.com.au/collections/bar-accessories?pf_t_category=style_Cocktail+Shaker" class="">cocktail shaker</a> is a must-have for any home bar setup. It will allow you to mix and shake drinks to perfection. Minimax offers a range of cocktail shakers, including stainless steel options, which are both stylish and durable. You’ll also need a quality <a href="https://www.minimax.com.au/collections/bar-accessories?pf_t_category=style_Strainer" class="">strainer</a> too.</p><p><br></p><p data-handle="chef_inox_speed_pourer">Another essential tool that you'll need to ensure that your drinks are perfectly balanced is a jigger or measuring cup. Minimax offers a range of jiggers in different sizes and materials, including stainless steel and copper. Of course, if you’re a bit of a free spirit, wield some mixology magic with a <a href="https://www.minimax.com.au/products/chef_inox_speed_pourer" class="" data-bss-pl="active">speed pourer</a> and get those drinks out quick, fast.</p><p><br></p><p>A bar spoon is also a useful accessory in your home bar setup. It can be used for stirring cocktails and layering ingredients. Minimax offers a range of bar spoons in various designs, including twisted and spiral options.</p><p><br></p><p>You can also keep your bubbly cold with a Minimax <a href="https://www.minimax.com.au/collections/party-tubs-ice-buckets" class="">party tub and ice bucket</a>. Oh, and if you like your drinks on the rocks, <a href="https://www.minimax.com.au/collections/bar-accessories?pf_t_category=style_Tongs" class="">ice tongs</a> are a must.</p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" id="r-1681171394480" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1681171394480" data-extraclass="" data-layout-lg="12" d