dant lights above your bar to create a warm, inviting atmosphere.</p><p></p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1685689123361" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1685689123361"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">Personalising Your Bar</h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1682918342572" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1682918342572" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>Become a bar <a href="https://www.minimax.com.au/collections/decorator" class="">decorator</a>. Add personal touches like a customised sign, your favourite artwork or <a href="https://www.minimax.com.au/collections/photo-frames" class="">photos</a>, or even a small chalkboard to write drink specials or fun messages for your guests.</p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1685689238920" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1685689238920"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">Add Some Greenery</h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1685689243288" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1685689243288" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>Plants can add a touch of natural beauty to any space. Consider adding some potted herbs or succulents to your home bar to add some greenery and freshness with Minimax <a href="https://www.minimax.com.au/collections/pots-planters" class="">pots and planters</a>.</p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1685689290330" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1685689290330"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">Considering your theme</h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1685689294123" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1685689294123" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>If you have a favourite cocktail or type of alcohol, consider building your home bar setup around a theme. For example, you could create a tiki bar theme with tropical decor and fun, fruity cocktails or a whisky bar theme with leather accents and rich, smokey drinks.</p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" id="r-1685689376827" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1685689376827" data-extraclass="" data-layout-lg="12" data-layout-md="12" data-layout-sm="12" data-layout-xs="12" style="display: block;"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-12 gf_col-md-12 gf_col-sm-12 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1614760291866" data-id="1614760291866"><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" id="r-1685689376889" class="gf_row gf_row-gap-0" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1685689376889" data-extraclass="" data-row-gap="0px" style=""><div class="gf_col-lg-12 gf_column" id="c-1615178530067" data-id="1615178530067"><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1685689376796" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1685689376796"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">Things To Avoid</h2></div></div><div data-label="Separator" data-key="separator" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1685689376877" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-separator" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1685689376877"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-align="left" data-exc=""><hr class="gf_separator"></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1685689376761" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1685689376761"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">Overspending</h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1685689376746" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1685689376746" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>Going all-out when setting up a home bar can be tempting, but overspending can quickly drain your budget. Stick to the essentials and build up your collection over time.</p><p></p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1685689376758" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1685689376758"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">Not Investing In Quality Tools And Glassware</h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1685689376773" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1685689376773" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>That being said, investing in quality tools and glassware can make a big difference in the taste and presentation of your cocktails. Cheap or low-quality tools and glassware can lead to subpar drinks and a less enjoyable experience, so find a happy medium between cost and quality.</p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1685689376875" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1685689376875"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">Not Considering Storage</h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1685689376845" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1685689376845" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>Proper storage is essential to keep your spirits and other ingredients fresh and accessible. Ensure you have enough space to store your collection, and consider investing in a storage solution, such as a bar cabinet or shelf.</p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1685689376838" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1685689376838"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">Not Experimenting With New Ingredients</h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1685689376816" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1685689376816" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>One of the joys of having a home bar is experimenting with fresh ingredients and flavours. Don't be afraid to try new spirits, mixers, and bitters to create unique and delicious cocktails.</p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1685689487432" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1685689487432"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">Neglecting to learn the basics</h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1685689493959" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1685689493959" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>While it's fun to experiment and try new things, learning the basics of cocktail-making, including the proper measurements, techniques, and equipment is essential. Taking the time to learn the fundamentals will help you create better cocktails and avoid mistakes.</p><p></p><p></p><p></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" id="r-1681172747896" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1681172747896" data-extraclass="" data-layout-lg="12" data-layout-md="12" data-layout-sm="12" data-layout-xs="12" style="display: block;"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-12 gf_col-md-12 gf_col-sm-12 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1614760291866" data-id="1614760291866"><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" id="r-1681172747997" class="gf_row gf_row-gap-0" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1681172747997" data-extraclass="" data-row-gap="0px" style=""><div class="gf_col-lg-12 gf_column" id="c-1615178530067" data-id="1615178530067"><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1681172747882" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1681172747882"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">Home Bar Maintenance</h2></div></div><div data-label="Separator" data-key="separator" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1681172747847" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-separator" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1681172747847"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-align="left" data-exc=""><hr class="gf_separator"></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" id="e-1685947090820" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1685947090820" data-resolution="3000x3000" style=""><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/59188b64-d532-4c19-a4ef-80469e29daea/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/_DSC3353.jpg" alt="The Ultimate DIY Home Bar Setup | Minimax Blog" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="1200" natural-height="625" width="1200" height="625"></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1681172747954" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1681172747954" style=""><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>Properly cleaning and maintaining your bar accessories and glassware is essential to keeping them in good condition and ensuring that your cocktails taste their best. Here are some tips to help you clean and maintain your bar accessories and glassware:</p><p><br></p><p>•&nbsp; Hand wash your glassware</p><p>•&nbsp; Dry glassware thoroughly to avoid water spots and streaks</p><p>•&nbsp; Use a polishing cloth for extra shine</p><p>•&nbsp; Clean your bar accessories regularly</p><p>•&nbsp; Avoid using abrasive cleaners; lint-free cloths or a microfiber towel are recommended</p><p>•&nbsp; Store your glassware and bar accessories properly, preferably away from sunlight</p><p></p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" id="r-1685689683926" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1685689683926" data-extraclass="" data-layout-lg="12" data-layout-md="12" data-layout-sm="12" data-layout-xs="12" style="display: block;"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-12 gf_col-md-12 gf_col-sm-12 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1614760291866" data-id="1614760291866"><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" id="r-1685689683849" class="gf_row gf_row-gap-0" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1685689683849" data-extraclass="" data-row-gap="0px" style=""><div class="gf_col-lg-12 gf_column" id="c-1615178530067" data-id="1615178530067"><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1685689683838" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1685689683838"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">Your Dream Home Bar</h2></div></div><div data-label="Separator" data-key="separator" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1685689683983" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-separator" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1685689683983"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-align="left" data-exc=""><hr class="gf_separator"></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" id="e-1685947351208" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1685947351208" data-resolution="3000x3000" style=""><